text:
Aromat - karmel, mleczna czekolada, piernik, cappuccino, kawy dość mało; palonych nut brak.
Piana - obfita, drobna i średnia, beżowa;
Smak - słodki, dużo karmelu, lekka kawowa kwaskowość, czekolada gorzka. Finisz wytrawny, czekoladowo kawowy i lekko ściągający. Za wysokie wysycenie, które szczypie w język i nie pozwala cieszyć się fakturą, którą powinny nadać płatki owsiane.

Cor negra com espuma bege cremosa de baixa formação e persistência de uma camada espessa e pouco lacing;
Aroma de baunilha, chocolate e café;
Sabor de início de chocolate amargo com meio de café e final de café com leve amargor; retrogosto deixando uma sensação aveludada na boca de baunilha e leve amargor;
Corpo sedoso e baixa carbonatação.

AROMA: slight note of puke (it pursue me today), nothing else, poorly ;( ;
APPEARANCE: black opaque/ ruby and clear under intensive light, very very rich, wonderful, but quite quickly dropping small-and-medium-bubble beige head, delightful lacing;
TASTE:indeed sweet, low bitterness, note of sourness, malt, little roastiness, very little chocolate;
PALATE: medium carbonation, also medium body, sweet-and-sour finish;
OVERALL: totally normal sweet stout, I was a bit loaded while sampling , so take amendment on it;
BEERS EXPIRATION DATE: dec 2014
ANOTHER NUMBER: L13269
